\| c - d\|^2 = \| c\|^2 + \|d \|^2 - 2cd
\left\| \frac{X}{\|X\|^2} \right\|^2 = \frac{1}{\|X\|^2}
cd := \langle c,d \rangle
\mathbb R^n
\lVert c-d\rVert^2 = \langle c-d, c-d \rangle  = \langle c,c \rangle - 2 \Re(\langle c,d\rangle )+ \langle d,d\rangle = \lVert c \rVert^2 + \lVert d \rVert ^2 -2cd
